### Render (Docker): cloud without Ollama
### Copy keys below into Dashboard → LightRAG service → Environment.
### You already set DeepSeek — keep LLM_* ; add EMBEDDING_* if documents still fail with "connect to Ollama".
### Delete any Render vars that point to Ollama or localhost:11434.

HOST=0.0.0.0
PORT=9621

### LLM — DeepSeek (OpenAI-compatible). Replace YOUR_DEEPSEEK_KEY in Render (Secret).
LLM_BINDING=openai
LLM_BINDING_HOST=https://api.deepseek.com/v1
LLM_BINDING_API_KEY=YOUR_DEEPSEEK_KEY
LLM_MODEL=deepseek-chat

### Embeddings — OpenAI (separate from Whisper; same platform account is fine). Use sk-... API key.
EMBEDDING_BINDING=openai
EMBEDDING_BINDING_HOST=https://api.openai.com/v1
EMBEDDING_BINDING_API_KEY=YOUR_OPENAI_SK_KEY
EMBEDDING_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small
EMBEDDING_DIM=1536
EMBEDDING_TOKEN_LIMIT=8192
EMBEDDING_SEND_DIM=false

### Optional: protect API (Telegram bot sends X-API-Key)
# LIGHTRAG_API_KEY=your-secure-api-key-here

### REMOVE from Render if present (these force Ollama and break on Render):
# LLM_BINDING=ollama
# LLM_BINDING_HOST=http://localhost:11434
# EMBEDDING_BINDING=ollama
# EMBEDDING_BINDING_HOST=http://localhost:11434
# EMBEDDING_BINDING_HOST=http://host.docker.internal:11434
